Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Provides: ${python:Provides}
Description: Python API for popular chan boards
 Chan Grabber is a Python framework for creating network applications
 to interact with chan boards which provide JSON API like 4Chan. It is
 very simple to use and provide a way to download images, posts and
 comments from the chan.

Package: chan-grabber
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
	 python-chan (= ${binary:Version})
Description: 4Chan image downloader
 Chan Grabber is a Python framework for creating network applications
 to interact with chan boards which provide JSON API like 4Chan. It is
 very simple to use and provide a way to download images, posts and
 comments from the chan.
 .
 This application is an example of use of python-chan library and
 let you download images from 4Chan.
